{
  "id": "5b22fe5a580efc0014cbb54e",
  "title": "Scrapboxと長文",
  "created": 1529020003,
  "updated": 1642212675,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5b22fe63aff09e0000520017",
      "text": "Scrapboxと長文",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529020003,
      "updated": 1529020250
    },
    {
      "id": "61e22971aff09e00001a3d2c",
      "text": "2018-09-12",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1642211697,
      "updated": 1642211704
    },
    {
      "id": "5b22fe5a580efc0014cbb54e",
      "text": "[長文]の書籍を頭から読んでいくのは、人の話を[一方的に聞]いているのと同じ、[一次元的]な言葉",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529020003,
      "updated": 1536685314
    },
    {
      "id": "5b22fe92aff09e000052001a",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/dd65b2c5a2226aa0d873cecff868a4a7]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529020050,
      "updated": 1529020050
    },
    {
      "id": "5b22fe91aff09e0000520019",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529020049,
      "updated": 1529020049
    },
    {
      "id": "5b22fe6baff09e0000520018",
      "text": "[速読]をする人はまず[目次]を読んで[ツリー構造]を頭に入れてから",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529020011,
      "updated": 1536685324
    },
    {
      "id": "5b22ff03aff09e000052001d",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/d0cfd10df8810722bd63da61a3960763]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529020164,
      "updated": 1529020164
    },
    {
      "id": "5b22ff02aff09e000052001c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529020163,
      "updated": 1529020163
    },
    {
      "id": "5b22fee5aff09e000052001b",
      "text": "その後本文を読んで、本文から得られた断片を結びつけていく",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529020133,
      "updated": 1529020234
    },
    {
      "id": "5b22ff4caff09e0000520020",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/6f5c6adee994f0ddac4ef67fcb007725]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529020236,
      "updated": 1529020236
    },
    {
      "id": "5b22ff4aaff09e000052001f",
      "text": "これは[ネットワークを組み立て]ていく言語の使い方",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529020235,
      "updated": 1536685337
    },
    {
      "id": "5b23083eaff09e0000d8e820",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529022527,
      "updated": 1529022527
    },
    {
      "id": "5b230b1eaff09e0000d1e927",
      "text": "逆に長文を一次元的に読みたい人向けには、1ページに全部入れるか、各章のページに「次の章」というリンクを作るかしかない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529023262,
      "updated": 1529023322
    },
    {
      "id": "5b230b5daff09e0000d1e928",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529023326,
      "updated": 1529023326
    },
    {
      "id": "61e22d3faff09e00003174fe",
      "text": "[Scrapbox]は[ネットワーク的言語]の扱いに長けたツール",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1642212672,
      "updated": 1642212675
    },
    {
      "id": "5b230883aff09e0000d8e821",
      "text": "[一次元的長文]を単にScrapboxに入れようとするのではなく、その長文に対する読書メモの形でキーワードや見出しを抜き出し、箇条書きアウトラインにするのが良いのではないだろうか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529022595,
      "updated": 1536685349
    },
    {
      "id": "5b230c01aff09e0000d1e929",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529023490,
      "updated": 1529023490
    },
    {
      "id": "5b22ff34aff09e000052001e",
      "text": "このプロセスを[インクリメンタル]にしたい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529020212,
      "updated": 1536685360
    },
    {
      "id": "5b230c64aff09e0000d1e92b",
      "text": " まず長文を貼る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529023588,
      "updated": 1529023598
    },
    {
      "id": "5b230c6eaff09e0000d1e92c",
      "text": " 抜き書きしていく",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529023598,
      "updated": 1529023619
    },
    {
      "id": "5b230c83aff09e0000d1e92d",
      "text": "  抜き書きを支援するカスタマイズが必要",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529023619,
      "updated": 1529023648
    },
    {
      "id": "5b230ca0aff09e0000d1e92e",
      "text": "  元の文章を切り取るのではなく複製し、行パーマリンクで出展を示す",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529023648,
      "updated": 1529025440
    },
    {
      "id": "61e22893aff09e00003174ea",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1642211476,
      "updated": 1642211488
    },
    {
      "id": "61e22894aff09e00003174eb",
      "text": "[一次元の文章]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1642211477,
      "updated": 1642211505
    },
    {
      "id": "61e228acaff09e00003174ec",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1642211501,
      "updated": 1642211501
    }
  ]
}